These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, january
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Birthday   | march | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, bartender
1. the bartender is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Job   | analyst | bartender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | drawing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-4::.
